1
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:55,400
I thought you wouldn't come.

2
00:00:55,660 --> 00:00:57,160
I promised you.

3
00:00:57,380 --> 00:00:58,860
Sorry I'm late.

4
00:03:04,780 --> 00:03:05,640
New talent selection.

5
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:06,740
I agree to launch it.

6
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:11,040
Nice one, Old Zhou.

7
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,200
You've come to your senses.

8
00:03:13,940 --> 00:03:15,480
You wait, I'll notify everyone right away.

9
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:16,500
Three conditions.

10
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:18,520
First.

11
00:03:18,900 --> 00:03:19,940
No commercial open auditions.

12
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:21,600
Switch to an internal nomination system.

13
00:03:22,540 --> 00:03:25,840
Board members, senior management, even all employees can nominate.

14
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:27,120
Internal?

15
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:29,400
Second.

16
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,160
All contestants

17
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,880
must wear masks throughout the entire process.

18
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:34,900
I don't look at faces,

19
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:35,840
don't listen to stories.

20
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:37,040
I only choose voices.

21
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,080
Wait, wait.

22
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,480
The marketing department won't agree.

23
00:03:40,940 --> 00:03:41,900
Not showing faces?

24
00:03:42,060 --> 00:03:42,820
How do I do styling?

25
00:03:42,820 --> 00:03:43,620
How do I build hype?

26
00:03:43,620 --> 00:03:45,040
A good voice has nothing to do with appearance.

27
00:03:45,100 --> 00:03:46,640
I am only responsible for the voice itself.

28
00:03:47,500 --> 00:03:48,340
Third.

29
00:03:49,460 --> 00:03:51,600
I have the final say on who gets chosen.

30
00:03:52,500 --> 00:03:55,200
Do you already have someone in mind?

31
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:56,400
You can just say it.

32
00:03:57,040 --> 00:03:58,640
Last time you told me

33
00:03:58,640 --> 00:04:00,340
you've been waiting for a voice

34
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:01,840
that moves you.

35
00:04:02,100 --> 00:04:03,060
To be honest,

36
00:04:03,700 --> 00:04:05,200
have you already found it?

37
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,400
Yes.

38
00:04:08,060 --> 00:04:09,400
Then just decide directly.

39
00:04:09,660 --> 00:04:11,040
With your ability and resources,

40
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:12,600
isn't it easy to make someone a star?

41
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:14,140
Why drag the whole company into

42
00:04:14,140 --> 00:04:15,740
putting on this kind of masked show?

43
00:04:16,140 --> 00:04:17,360
Precisely because I found her,

44
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:19,320
I can't just sign her privately like that.

45
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:21,460
I need to let her voice

46
00:04:21,820 --> 00:04:23,420
cut through all the labels

47
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:24,460
and prejudices,

48
00:04:25,420 --> 00:04:26,580
clean and pure,

49
00:04:27,060 --> 00:04:28,260
winning for everyone to hear.

50
00:04:49,100 --> 00:04:49,600
Xingyao,

51
00:04:50,060 --> 00:04:51,100
you'll never guess.

52
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,000
Star River Music

53
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:53,800
is holding a masked singer selection.

54
00:04:55,940 --> 00:04:58,020
Only voice, no face, Xingyao.

55
00:04:58,420 --> 00:04:59,860
This is made for you.

56
00:05:00,780 --> 00:05:01,900
You can go give it a try.

57
00:05:03,660 --> 00:05:04,960
I don't sing anymore.

58
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:06,200
Why?

59
00:05:07,260 --> 00:05:08,760
You've persisted for so many years.

60
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:10,820
Now that the opportunity has finally come,

61
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,900
don't you want to give it a try?

62
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,160
If you wear a mask for too long,

63
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:20,400
there will come a day when you have to take it off.

64
00:05:21,900 --> 00:05:22,700
Xiu Jie.

65
00:05:24,860 --> 00:05:25,920
I really don't sing anymore.

66
00:05:27,900 --> 00:05:29,560
You finally have a chance to shine,

67
00:05:30,220 --> 00:05:32,100
yet you insist on hiding yourself.

68
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:33,800
Xingyao,

69
00:05:34,860 --> 00:05:36,160
I really don't understand you.

70
00:06:01,020 --> 00:06:01,860
Sorry.

71
00:06:03,500 --> 00:06:04,500
I did my best.

72
00:06:20,860 --> 00:06:21,700
Is anyone there?

73
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:28,800
I'm still inside.

74
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:36,260
Sing for me right now.

75
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,260
Let's meet.

76
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,500
I want to talk with you.

77
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:58,880
I'm not —

78
00:06:59,080 --> 00:06:59,840
not really convenient right now.

79
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,840
Where are you? What happened?

80
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,080
N-nothing.

81
00:07:05,220 --> 00:07:05,920
Li Xingyao,

82
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:07,400
tell me your current location.

83
00:07:07,660 --> 00:07:08,260
Right now.

84
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:10,360
I'm in the screening room of a cinema.

85
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:12,600
The d-door is locked.

86
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:15,620
You stay there, don't move.

87
00:07:15,620 --> 00:07:16,240
I'll be there right away.

88
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,400
Xiao Yao.

89
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:02,640
Xiao Yao.

90
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:03,440
Xiao Yao.

91
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:04,760
Xiao Yao.

92
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,080
Xiao Yao, it's me.

93
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:06,960
It's me, Xiao Yao.

94
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,520
Xiao Yao.

95
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,300
It's okay.

96
00:08:16,220 --> 00:08:17,020
It's okay.

97
00:08:38,940 --> 00:08:39,440
Here.

98
00:08:43,020 --> 00:08:43,960
It's sweetened.

99
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:45,000
Drink up.

100
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:50,160
You still remember...

101
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:58,180
How could I not remember?

102
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:35,740
Where is this?

103
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:37,680
My home.

104
00:10:27,800 --> 00:10:29,420
So all these more than ten years,

105
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,220
you thought I just left for good

106
00:10:31,220 --> 00:10:32,600
and completely forgot about you, is that it?

107
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:34,800
Isn't that the case?

108
00:10:36,800 --> 00:10:37,460
No.

109
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:41,100
Wait a moment.

110
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:49,120
All these more than ten years,

111
00:10:49,620 --> 00:10:51,060
every one of your birthdays,

112
00:10:51,420 --> 00:10:52,260
every New Year,

113
00:10:52,260 --> 00:10:53,660
I wrote you letters.

114
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,800
But they were all returned.

115
00:10:56,740 --> 00:10:58,060
I also went looking for you,

116
00:10:59,260 --> 00:11:00,700
but I couldn't find you.

117
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:16,900
I didn't forget.

118
00:11:19,520 --> 00:11:20,780
Not for a single day.

119
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:24,560
I'm sorry.

120
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:28,220
I should be the one saying sorry.

121
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:33,280
If I had tried a little harder to find you back then,

122
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:36,300
you wouldn't have had to suffer so much alone.

123
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,400
I also promised you

124
00:11:40,620 --> 00:11:41,640
that I would protect you.

125
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,020
I'm sorry.

126
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:49,060
You still remember?

127
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:51,080
I remember.

128
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,200
Of course I remember everything.

129
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:57,800
But this promise, delayed for so many years —

130
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:00,440
are you willing to believe in it once more?

131
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:09,920
I've missed you so much.

132
00:12:11,420 --> 00:12:12,560
Every single day.

133
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:14,520
I know.

134
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:32,180
You wrote this?

135
00:12:35,880 --> 00:12:36,400
Here.

136
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:38,760
Look, the letter I wrote to you.

137
00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:43,120
Xiao Yao,

138
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:44,360
I moved.

139
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:45,640
In the provincial capital.

140
00:12:45,880 --> 00:12:46,880
New address:

141
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:49,360
Guangming Road, South District, Provincial Capital,

142
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:51,160
No. 17, Building 3, Apartment 201.

143
00:12:51,760 --> 00:12:52,200
Phone number:

144
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:54,360
0571-8642XXX
0571-8642XXX.

145
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:56,800
You must write to me.

146
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:58,500
Tell me how you've been

147
00:12:58,560 --> 00:13:00,120
what scores you get on exams,

148
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,760
whether anyone bullies you.

149
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:04,080
I promised to protect you.

150
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:05,040
Even if we're far apart,

151
00:13:05,040 --> 00:13:05,960
I will still do it.

152
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:07,920
If you get bullied,

153
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:10,360
even if I have to take a train, I'll come back and beat them up.

154
00:13:11,160 --> 00:13:11,580
Also,

155
00:13:11,580 --> 00:13:12,800
don't forget our promise.

156
00:13:13,220 --> 00:13:14,560
Don't give up singing.

157
00:13:15,400 --> 00:13:17,140
I will become a very talented producer,

158
00:13:17,280 --> 00:13:18,920
write the best songs for you.

159
00:13:19,560 --> 00:13:20,720
Wait for me to come back to you.

160
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:22,160
For sure.

161
00:13:23,160 --> 00:13:24,040
Zhou Jing'an.

162
00:13:24,280 --> 00:13:26,540
August 23, 2009.

163
00:13:41,820 --> 00:13:43,720
You really did become a very talented producer.

164
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:47,400
What about you?

165
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:49,300
Me?

166
00:13:53,800 --> 00:13:54,460
I...

167
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:01,560
Why did you give up?

168
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:05,260
Maybe I'm just not cut out for this path.

169
00:14:08,820 --> 00:14:09,400
Look.

170
00:14:13,400 --> 00:14:15,360
I've listened to all of your songs.

171
00:14:16,260 --> 00:14:18,760
See, even when you hide yourself away,

172
00:14:18,760 --> 00:14:20,220
I can still find you.

173
00:14:22,460 --> 00:14:23,040
So

174
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:27,700
if you were going to give up, you would have done it long ago.

175
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:29,200
The reason you've held on till now

176
00:14:29,260 --> 00:14:30,160
is precisely because

177
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:32,060
is precisely because

178
00:14:32,060 --> 00:14:34,080
music is a very important part of you, isn't it?

179
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:37,620
If because of those

180
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:39,620
people who hurt you

181
00:14:39,620 --> 00:14:42,460
you're going to completely forget the former Li Xingyao,

182
00:14:43,760 --> 00:14:46,020
why are you being so cruel to yourself?

183
00:14:47,460 --> 00:14:48,580
I've tried.

184
00:14:49,220 --> 00:14:51,220
But right now, I really can't.

185
00:14:51,220 --> 00:14:52,720
I can't sing in front of people.

186
00:14:53,020 --> 00:14:54,600
As soon as there are people, I feel

187
00:14:57,160 --> 00:14:58,220
extremely uncomfortable.

188
00:15:04,220 --> 00:15:05,020
Look at me.

189
00:15:07,680 --> 00:15:09,020
Come back to my side.

190
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:12,260
We'll face it together.

191
00:15:14,460 --> 00:15:16,500
What I failed to do before,

192
00:15:16,880 --> 00:15:19,360
I'll make up for you, one by one.

193
00:15:20,460 --> 00:15:21,700
Hold on a little longer,

194
00:15:22,280 --> 00:15:22,860
okay?

195
00:15:24,300 --> 00:15:25,960
Do you really believe I can do it?

196
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:29,960
You are someone who has experienced darkness.

197
00:15:30,520 --> 00:15:32,680
Even darkness couldn't swallow you.

198
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:34,940
You are, in my heart,

199
00:15:35,500 --> 00:15:36,260
the bravest.

200
00:15:57,400 --> 00:15:58,720
If you say I can,

201
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:02,360
Then I am willing to believe in myself again.

202
00:20:32,040 --> 00:20:33,960
He has never proactively recommended anyone before.

203
00:20:34,120 --> 00:20:35,880
The boss actually recommended him

204
00:20:45,120 --> 00:20:48,080
I am always learning to be alone--

205
00:20:48,280 --> 00:20:51,320
Dusk of four seasons for one person

206
00:20:52,280 --> 00:20:55,560
A person tastes the salty and the mild.

207
00:20:55,560 --> 00:20:58,460
A person's body temperature
